  'inventory' as tabela, COUNT(*) as registros_null 
FROM inventory WHERE tenantId IS NULL
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  'warehouseLocations' as tabela, COUNT(*) as registros_null 
FROM warehouseLocations WHERE tenantId IS NULL
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  'products' as tabela, COUNT(*) as registros_null 
FROM products WHERE tenantId IS NULL;
